# 운영 canonical URL (끝 슬래시 없음). 메타·사이트맵·robots·구조화 데이터에 사용.
# 커스텀 도메인이 있으면 반드시 그 주소로 고정(중복 canonical 방지).
# 미설정 시 Vercel은 VERCEL_URL로 대체( *.vercel.app ).
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-domain.vercel.app

# Shown on /contact (mailto link)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTACT_EMAIL=you@example.com

# Optional: default OG/Twitter image (absolute URL)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_OG_IMAGE_URL=https://your-domain.vercel.app/og.png

# Optional: Google AdSense (enable adsbygoogle + slots)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_CLIENT_ID=ca-pub-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_HOME=xxxxxxxxxx
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_TOP=xxxxxxxxxx
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_BETWEEN=xxxxxxxxxx
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_MID_GUIDE=xxxxxxxxxx
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_INLINE=xxxxxxxxxx
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_FOOTER=xxxxxxxxxx
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_BELOW_RELATED=xxxxxxxxxx
